text:
@brad_rando @thechriscorica @scottmelker We took rides up to Palm Harbor, etc. because the Red Tide doesn't make it up that far (very rare). Crowded up there....(the big roads)....my wife likes beach and I like sailing so at Minimum we'd like to be within 20 minutes of both.
Red Tide =much bigger deal than "advertised"
description: Truly do know most Everything. Polymath. Many moons of Experience. AMA (Twitter for 10+ years...quit for a while). If you knew who I was...
